    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >备受 400 万玩家喜爱的经典大奖之作《逃脱学院》再谱新章，《逃脱学院 2：再返校园》终于来了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到逃脱学院，这里业界首屈一指的密室专家将会教授各位最为顶尖的逃脱之道。无论新老同学，全体目光这边看齐。革新密室经典，《逃脱学院 2：再返校园》将前作中的密室逃脱模式彻底进化升级：首款开放世界密室逃脱游戏横空出世！在家即可轻松体验！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>密室逃脱大师精心打造赛博密室</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296060/extras/243cccf1a200c0ff508793729354e616.poster.avif?t=1765306436\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296060/extras/243cccf1a200c0ff508793729354e616.webm?t=1765306436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296060/extras/243cccf1a200c0ff508793729354e616.mp4?t=1765306436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《逃脱学院 2：再返校园》带着全新战役重磅归来，谜题设计领域资深专家团队倾力打造业界顶尖密室逃脱场景。然而脱离了现实世界的沉闷束缚，《逃脱学院 2：再返校园》的解谜好像有些不是那么安全：怎么还有刺顶天花板啊？检查。落差 100 英尺？检查。没想到最可怕的竟然是……期末考试？仔细检查。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >教学惊险刺激，课程荒诞不经，在咱们这所学院里，果然还是搭上命的生死考验更有学习效率呀。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索活着的校园</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296060/extras/8016a921a60a8b72f77ba4b36764ec40.poster.avif?t=1765306436\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296060/extras/8016a921a60a8b72f77ba4b36764ec40.webm?t=1765306436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296060/extras/8016a921a60a8b72f77ba4b36764ec40.mp4?t=1765306436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《逃脱学院 2》，校园本身就是一个巨大的密室。课间时分，不妨探索一下广袤的枢纽区域，那里机密重重，遍布各种秘密空间、各种隐匿隧道，更有致命的陷阱虎视眈眈。或者也可以和好伙伴们放松一下，毕竟怎么也得体验一把校园<i>*青春*</i>呀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论怎样，这所学院都会是你离家之后的全新港湾。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>拉上同学一起开启这场线上合作抑或本地同屏的密室逃脱之旅</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296060/extras/2c7b051acecd74facdb2abde3da1df71.poster.avif?t=1765306436\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296060/extras/2c7b051acecd74facdb2abde3da1df71.webm?t=1765306436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >朋友一起逃，密室嗨翻天。《逃脱学院 2》支持线上联机与本地同屏游玩哦。新增不计时模式可选，无论新手高手，自成步调轻松解谜。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开启全新故事之旅</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296060/extras/2019ec20f138dd50b7528044d1f091cc.poster.avif?t=1765306436\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296060/extras/2019ec20f138dd50b7528044d1f091cc.webm?t=1765306436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296060/extras/2019ec20f138dd50b7528044d1f091cc.mp4?t=1765306436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《逃脱学院 2》全新剧情，新老玩家都有共鸣！围绕学校创立伊始的黑暗秘密在你面前徐徐展开，学院的本质必将引出震撼的真相。在课程扩增、角色驱动叙事以及充满谜题的支线任务中结识新老师，与初代中的熟悉面孔迎来重逢！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>再返校园！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296060/extras/8f67cbf91d3097e2ceff3b26aa0feb1b.poster.avif?t=1765306436\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296060/extras/8f67cbf91d3097e2ceff3b26aa0feb1b.webm?t=1765306436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296060/extras/8f67cbf91d3097e2ceff3b26aa0feb1b.mp4?t=1765306436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本次《逃脱学院》续作精心打造画面风格、海量细节、全新环境，甚至为教授和学生准备了时尚的全新装束哦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，邪恶 DJ 天才 Doseone 再度回归，带来全新超棒节奏音乐，学习放松都要有所享受！全新原声配乐，解谜气氛顶顶到位！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还等什么呢？是时候……再返校园了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
